-- Rohm CEO says no settlement with Dow Chemical yet
-- 
-- Mon Mar 9, 2009 3:28pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/03/09/us-rohm-dow-ceo-idUSTRE5285VU20090309

 

 GEORGETOWN, Delaware  (Reuters) - Rohm and Haas Co ROH.N Chief Executive Raj Gupta said his company has not yet reached a settlement with Dow Chemical Co ( DOW.N ) over Dow's soured takeover of Rohm. 

 Walking out of the courtroom on Monday afternoon, Gupta said that no agreement had been reached yet. (Reporting by  Michael Erman , editing by Richard Chang)